body:
No.  The analysis takes less than a second, as the logs show.  The whole test was supposed to take only five seconds, but the change 8239116d598cef15982af82eed790944f82fa3a4, which I wasn't aware of till now, bumped the timeout to 5 minutes and added the -index flag, which makes it very slow and causes it to use ~1GB memory.

Gerrit: https://go-review.googlesource.com/#/c/7267/
